text: Nothofagus discoidea is a species of plant in the Nothofagaceae family. It is endemic to New Caledonia. ==References== * Jaffré, T. et al. 1998. Nothofagus discoidea. 2006 IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. Downloaded on 22 August 2007.
